name: Exploring Silver City
description:
Spend your day in charming Silver City of Kotagede.
Explore one of undiscovered places for holiday in Yogyakarta is the best choice for your day.

We will see how to makejewelry around Kotagede, and then visit one of the most famous Chocolate places in Yogyakarta, then Historical Place in Mosque Mataram. If we have extra time, I will introduce you tolocal people around Kotagede.
